def runChain(n:Nat, f:(Key, a) -> a, key:Key, x0:a) -> Fin n => a given (a|Data) =
  ref <- with_state x0
  for i:(Fin n).
    prev = get ref
    new = ixkey key i | f(get ref)
    ref := new
    new

    new
